Description: Nasty NAS storage plugin for Proxmox VE
 Provides shared VM block storage over iSCSI and NVMe/TCP using a Nasty
 NAS appliance. Manages bcachefs Block subvolumes via the Nasty JSON-RPC
 WebSocket API.
